reviewText: As a child, they will love it. Mine both request it on a daily basis. As an adult, you will find it odd. Babies with adult moving out of sync.  That being said, I won't go on a car ride over 5 hours without it.
This DVD is horrible. It will scare your baby if anything. It's just a bunch of babies with false lips moving up and down. Absolutely horrible!!!
You become mesmerized watching the singing babies.  Children of all ages watch it and adults are interested as well.  Nursery rhymes and prompts are used.

My nephew and niece love this video! ^^
It's such an excellent product!
Received so quickly as promised
I purchased this dvd for my daughter to use at her daycare and the children love it.
